---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Sponsorship Opportunities - Fells Prospect Community Association"
  description="Partner with FPCA to promote your local business. We offer business promotion on our website, newsletter, and events."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative py-20 md:py-28" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D4A574 0%, #B8914E 100%);">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8 shadow-2xl" style="background-color: #FAF8F4;">
        <svg class="w-12 h-12" style="color: #D4A574;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6" style="font-family: Georgia, serif; color: #3D3D3D;">
        Sponsorship Opportunities
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl max-w-3xl mx-auto" style="color: #3D3D3D;">
        Partner with FPCA to grow your business and support your community
      </p>
    </div>
    <!-- Decorative bottom -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 60" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-full">
        <path d="M0 0L60 5C120 10 240 20 360 23.3C480 27 600 23 720 21.7C840 20 960 20 1080 23.3C1200 27 1320 33 1380 36.7L1440 40V60H0V0Z" fill="#FAF8F4"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20" style="background-color: #FAF8F4;">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Partnership Info -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-10 md:p-14 mb-12" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #F5F1E8, #EFE9DC);">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-10">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6" style="font-family: Georgia, serif; color: #3D3D3D;">
              Partner with Our Community
            </h2>
            <div class="w-32 h-1 mx-auto mb-6" style="background-color: #D4A574;"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed" style="color: #3D3D3D;">
            <p>
              FPCA is interested in partnerships to promote our local businesses. We are an <strong style="color: #C1503D;">IRS registered 501(c)3 non-profit</strong> and <strong style="color: #C1503D;">State of Maryland charitable organization</strong>.
            </p>

            <div class="p-6 rounded-xl" style="background-color: #FAF8F4; border-left: 6px solid #1B365D;">
              <p class="font-semibold mb-2" style="color: #1B365D;">
                Get Your Business Visible
              </p>
              <p style="color: #3D3D3D;">
                We can get your business publicly visible in front of an engaged and local audience.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Benefits Section -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-10" style="font-family: Georgia, serif; color: #3D3D3D;">
          What We <span style="color: #C1503D;">Offer</span>
        </h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Website Promotion -->
          <div class="rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 text-center transition-transform hover:scale-105" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C1503D, #A84636); color: #FAF8F4;">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4" style="background-color: #D4A574;">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8" style="color: #3D3D3D;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">Website Promotion</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              Featured visibility on our community website reaching local residents and neighbors
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Newsletter -->
          <div class="rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 text-center transition-transform hover:scale-105" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1B365D, #4A7C9D); color: #FAF8F4;">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4" style="background-color: #D4A574;">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8" style="color: #3D3D3D;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">Monthly Newsletter</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              Exposure in our monthly newsletter distributed to engaged community members
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Events -->
          <div class="rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 text-center transition-transform hover:scale-105" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D4A574, #B8914E); color: #3D3D3D;">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4" style="background-color: #FAF8F4;">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8" style="color: #D4A574;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">Event Presence</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              Physical presence and recognition at our community events and gatherings
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact Section -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-10 md:p-14 text-center relative overflow-hidden" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1B365D 0%, #4A7C9D 100%); color: #FAF8F4;">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full opacity-5" style="background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, transparent 35px, rgba(250,248,244,.1) 35px, rgba(250,248,244,.1) 70px);"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6" style="background-color: #D4A574;">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10" style="color: #3D3D3D;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6" style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">
            Ready to Partner?
          </h2>

          <p class="text-xl mb-8" style="color: #EFE9DC;">
            For information about partnering with FPCA, please email us at:
          </p>

          <a
            href="mailto:sponsorship@FellsProspectCommunity.org"
            class="inline-block px-10 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg shadow-xl transition-all transform hover:scale-105 mb-6"
            style="background-color: #FAF8F4; color: #1B365D;"
            onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#EFE9DC'; this.style.boxShadow='0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)'"
            onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='#FAF8F4'; this.style.boxShadow='0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)'"
          >
            sponsorship@FellsProspectCommunity.org
          </a>

          <div class="mt-8 pt-8" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(197, 157, 95, 0.3);">
            <p class="text-sm" style="color: #D4A574;">
              We look forward to building a partnership that benefits your business and our community!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Additional CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #EFE9DC, #F5F1E8);">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6" style="font-family: Georgia, serif; color: #3D3D3D;">
        Questions About Sponsorship?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8" style="color: #3D3D3D;">
        We're happy to discuss custom partnership opportunities tailored to your business needs
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 font-semibold rounded-lg transition-all shadow-lg text-lg" style="background-color: #C1503D; color: #FAF8F4;" onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#A84636'" onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='#C1503D'">
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
